  Description
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  This software is an automation bot that monitors OpenZiti tunnel SDK
  releases, triggers builds of zgate-edge-tunnel via zgate-sdk-c-builder and
  zgate-tunnel-sdk-c-builder, and provides Telegram Bot integration for
  status queries, manual build triggers, and artifact download. It is
  developed and maintained by eCloudseal Inc.

